<TEXT>Your browser is unsupported We recommend using the latest version of IE11, Edge, Chrome, Firefox or Safari. It all starts with a single spark University of Illinois Chicago Search the site University of Illinois Chicago UIC Engineering Alumni Main Menu Expand News menu Expand Get Involved menu Expand Awards menu Eyebrow menu College of Engineering Engineering Career Center UIC menu UIC.edu Campus Map Search College of Engineering Down arrow icon Breadcrumbs UIC Engineering Alumni Get Involved Join us on LinkedIn Join us on LinkedIn UIC Engineering maintains a presence on LinkedIn in two ways that might interest alumni. Heading link xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"? Copy link This is UIC Engineering’s official private alumni group on LinkedIn. Follow the link below and request to join the group. We screen requests to make sure that all members have attended the College, creating a true sense of community online. The alumni group is a great place to post job opportunities, find former classmates, share news, learn about upcoming events that are open exclusively to alumni, and post about current issues in engineering or your particular industry. Please join us! Heading link xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"? Copy link The college’s public page on LinkedIn is designed primarily for people who are new to UIC—for example, prospective students and faculty—but alumni may enjoy the news feed that is located on this page below the “About us” box. Please “follow” this page (you should see a blue button in the left-hand column) so that our updates show up in your LinkedIn news feed. Alternatively, bookmark it and visit whenever you like. This also is a great page to suggest to your professional contacts who may be interested in serving as a partner to UIC Engineering. Get Involved Back to main content Join us on LinkedIn Alumni Mentoring Volunteer Engineer your own involvement Honor a Professor University of Illinois Chicago Contact 851 